examples: She attributes her success to hard work and a little luck.
Ella atribuye su éxito al trabajo duro y un poco de suerte.
The power failure was attributed to the recent storms and high winds.
El corte de energía se atribuyó a las recientes tormentas y fuertes vientos.
This play is usually attributed to Shakespeare.
Esta obra se suele atribuir a Shakespeare.
a quote that has often been falsely attributed to George Patton
una cita que a menudo se ha atribuido falsamente a George Patton
